rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0001
rows.name:
You sure know how to keep
a guy waiting, rookies.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0003
rows.name:
Is fault of Vandham for rushing
off ahead...

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0005
rows.name:
I guess you've already seen him when
we fought earlier, but let's introduce
ourselves properly, shall we?

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0009
rows.name:
I noticed you used an unusual
style of weapon?

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0010
rows.name:
Yeah, they're called Dual Scythes.
Even around here, I never met anyone
but Vandham who can use them.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0013
rows.name:
Don't flatter him too much.
He'll let it go to his head.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0014
rows.name: Vandham only have one Blade then?

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0016
rows.name:
I know most Drivers have a few, so they
can change up their strategies in battle,
but me, Suzaku's all I've ever needed!

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0019
rows.name:
Sounds to me like you just can't
be bothered to think up more than
one strategy, eh, old man?

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0021
rows.name:
Well, now that we all know each other,
let's get down to business.

rows.label: fev03_150_125_msg0023
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]An expert dodge, to be sure...
